Patch for Totem Player to use mouse wheel for volume control.
To install patched version on your system, issue following commands at terminal:

wget http://ftp.acc.umu.se/pub/GNOME/sources/totem/2.32/totem-2.32.0.tar.bz2
tar jxvf totem-2.32.0.tar.bz2
cd totem-2.32.0/
wget -qO- --no-check-certificate https://github.com/yappie/totem-wheel-volume/raw/master/main.patch | patch src/totem-object.c
./configure
make
sudo make install
cd ..
rm -rf totem-2.32.0/
rm -rf totem-2.32.0.tar.bz2
